{"_path":"/endorsement/html/canvas-svg","_dir":"html","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"Canvas 和 Svg","description":"","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"canvas"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Canvas"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"canvas 是画布，通过 js 来绘制 2D 图形，是逐像素进行渲染的，当其位置发生变化时，就会重新进行绘制。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"canvas 的特点如下："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"依赖分辨率"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不支持事件处理器"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"较弱的文本渲染能力"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"能够以 .png 或.jpg 的格式保存结果图像"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最适合图像密集型游戏，其中许多对象会被频繁重新绘制"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"矢量图也被称为面向对象的图像或绘图图像，在数学上定义为一系列由线连接的点。矢量文件中的图形元素称为对象，每个对象都是一个自称一体的实体，它具有颜色、形状、轮廓、大小和屏幕位置等属性"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"svg"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Svg"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"svg （Scalable Vector Graphics）是可缩放矢量图形，是基于可扩展标记语言 XML 描述的 2D 图形的语言，svg 基于 XML 就意味着 svg dom 中的每个元素都是可用的，可以为某个元素附加 js 事件处理器。在 svg 中，每个被绘制的图形均被视为对象。如果 svg 对象的属性发生变化，那么浏览器能够自动重现图形。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"svg 的特点如下："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不依赖分辨率"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"支持事件处理器"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最适合带有大型渲染区域的应用程序（比如谷歌地图）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"复杂度高会减慢渲染速度（任何过度使用 DOM 的应用程序速度都不是很快）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不适合游戏应用"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":5,"depth":5,"links":[{"id":"canvas","depth":2,"text":"Canvas"},{"id":"svg","depth":2,"text":"Svg"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:2.endorsement:8.html:canvas-svg.md","_source":"content","_file":"2.endorsement/8.html/canvas-svg.md","_extension":"md"}